WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:02.000
Welcome to Integrations.

00:02.000 --> 00:04.154
Step 1: Accounting Software.

00:04.154 --> 00:11.077
Connect Xero, MYOB, or QuickBooks to sync invoices, payments, and tax codes automatically.

00:11.077 --> 00:13.077
Step 2: Job Management.

00:13.077 --> 00:20.769
Integrate with ServiceM8, simPRO, or AroFlo to pull jobs, push updates, and keep everything in sync.

00:20.769 --> 00:22.846
Step 3: Calendar and Email.

00:22.846 --> 00:28.154
Google Calendar, Outlook, and SMTP email for automated notifications.

00:28.154 --> 00:30.615
Step 4: Analytics and Reporting.

00:30.615 --> 00:36.154
Connect Power BI, Google Analytics, or export CSV for custom dashboards.

00:36.154 --> 00:40.000
RestoreAssist becomes the hub of your entire operation.